HEADWORD: Unbraid
<hw>Un*braid"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>braid</ets>.]</ety> <def>To separate the strands
of; to undo, as a braid; to unravel; to disentangle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

